<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Relieving and Experience Letter</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Calibri', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-image: url('/assets/letterhead.jpeg'); /* ðŸ”¹ change to your letterhead absolute path */
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: 100% 100%; /* ensures full coverage */
      background-position: center top;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      width: 75%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      top: 240px; /* ðŸ”¹ adjust this value if content starts too high or low */
      font-size: 12pt;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #000;
    }

    .date {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 11pt;
    }

    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 13pt;
      text-decoration: underline;
      margin-bottom: 25px; /* adds little space after heading */
    }

    .paragraph {
      margin: 0 0 10pt 0;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 10pt;
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: left;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="content">
    <p class="date"><%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></p>

    <p class="title">Relieving and Experience Letter</p>

    <p class="paragraph"><strong>Employee Name:</strong> <%= employee_name %></p>
    <% if (employee_id) { %>
      <p class="paragraph"><strong>Employee ID:</strong> <%= employee_id %></p>
    <% } %>

    <p class="paragraph">This is with regard to your resignation,</p>

    <p class="paragraph">
      Dated <%= new Date(resignation_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %>
      from the position of <strong><%= designation %></strong> â€” We would like to inform you that you have been relieved of your duties at the end of business hours of
      <%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %>.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">
      We enjoyed working with you and thank you for the service rendered from
      <strong><%= new Date(start_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></strong>
      to
      <strong><%= new Date(relieving_date).toLocaleDateString('en-GB').replace(/\//g, '-') %></strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">We wish you good luck for future endeavours.</p>

    <p>Yours sincerely,<br>For Amazon IT Solutions</p>

    <% if (signaturePath) { %>
      <div style="margin-top: 8px;">
        <img src="<%= signaturePath %>" alt="Signature" style="width:85px; height:auto;" />
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <p class="signature"><%= hrName %></p>
    <p><strong><%= hrDesignation %></strong></p>

    <p class="note">Note: This is a computer-generated document. No Signature is required*</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
